name: I threw a sausage roll at his head because he called my sister a $lut!!! | The Adults Corner
summary: Episode 8 - We interview our first guest Julia.Julia is Cherry's younger sister and has supported her work career from a young age. Julia opens up about the bullying she received at school and in her workplace because of Cherry's Adult industry career choices.We also discuss how at the age of 22 she lost 1 of her ovaries which led her to doing egg freezing and the mental and emotional health impacts that she endured during these times.
